Package com.raihanMuhammadIhsanJBusAF

Class Algorithm

java.lang.Object
com.raihanMuhammadIhsanJBusAF.Algorithm
public class Algorithm extends Object
The Algorithm class contains methods that implement various useful algorithms for working with collections and arrays. It provides functionality such as collecting elements, counting occurrences, finding elements, checking existence, and pagination.

This class is not meant to be instantiated, as all its methods are static.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Raihan Muhammad Ihsan
